CollabText is a feature-rich collaborative document editing system that leverages the power of the MERN (MongoDB, Express.js, React.js, Node.js) stack. The platform provides a seamless user experience for creating, editing, and collaborating on documents in real-time. 

Key Features:

Real-time Editing:
Collaborate seamlessly with team members in real-time. Changes made by one user are instantly reflected for all collaborators, creating a dynamic and responsive editing environment.

MERN Stack Architecture:
Utilizes MongoDB as the database for storing document data, Express.js for the server-side logic, React.js for the user interface, and Node.js as the runtime environment. 

WebSocket Communication:
Implements WebSocket communication through socket.io for real-time updates. 

